#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:45
msgid ""
"If you would like to enforce the use of strong passwords, refer to <ulink "
"url=\"&blfs-book;postlfs/cracklib.html\"/> for installing CrackLib prior to "
"building Shadow. Then add <parameter>--with-libcrack</parameter> to the "
"<command>configure</command> command below."
msgstr ""
"Se você gostaria de reforçar o uso de senhas fortes, [então] recorra a "
"<ulink url=\"&blfs-book;postlfs/cracklib.html\"/> para instalar o CrackLib "
"antes de construir o Shadow. Então adicione <parameter>--with-libcrack</"
"parameter> ao comando <command>configure</command> abaixo."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:52
msgid ""
"Disable the installation of the <command>groups</command> program and its "
"man pages, as Coreutils provides a better version. Also, prevent the "
"installation of manual pages that were already installed in <xref "
"linkend=\"ch-system-man-pages\"/>:"
msgstr ""
"Desabilite a instalação do aplicativo <command>groups</command> e as páginas "
"de manual dele, uma vez que o Coreutils fornece uma versão melhor. Também, "
"impeça a instalação de páginas de manual que já foram instaladas no <xref "
"linkend=\"ch-system-man-pages\"/>:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:57
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i 's/groups$(EXEEXT) //' src/Makefile.in\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/groups\\.1 / /'   {} \\;\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/getspnam\\.3 / /' {} \\;\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/passwd\\.5 / /'   {} \\;</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -i 's/groups$(EXEEXT) //' src/Makefile.in\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/groups\\.1 / /'  {} \\;\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/getspnam\\.3 / /' {} \\;\n"
"find man -name Makefile.in -exec sed -i 's/passwd\\.5 / /'   {} \\"
";</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:62
msgid ""
"Instead of using the default <emphasis>crypt</emphasis> method, use the much "
"more secure <emphasis>YESCRYPT</emphasis> method of password encryption, "
"which also allows passwords longer than 8 characters.  It is also necessary "
"to change the obsolete <filename class=\"directory\">/var/spool/mail</"
"filename> location for user mailboxes that Shadow uses by default to the "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/var/mail</filename> location used currently. "
"And, remove <filename class=\"directory\">/bin</filename> and <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/sbin</filename> from the <envar>PATH</envar>, since "
"they are simply symlinks to their counterparts in <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Em vez de usar o método padrão <emphasis>crypt</emphasis>, use o método "
"muito mais seguro <emphasis>YESCRYPT</emphasis> de encriptação de senha, que "
"também permite senhas com mais de oito (08) caracteres. Também é necessário "
"mudar o local obsoleto <filename class=\"directory\">/var/spool/mail</"
"filename> para as caixas de correio de usuário(a) que o Shadow usa por "
"padrão para o local <filename class=\"directory\">/var/mail</filename> usado "
"atualmente. E, remova <filename class=\"directory\">/bin</filename> e "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/sbin</filename> do <envar>PATH</envar>, pois "
"eles são simplesmente links simbólicos para seus contrapartes em <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr</filename>."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:76
msgid ""
"If you wish to include <filename class=\"directory\">/bin</filename> and/or "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/sbin</filename> in the <envar>PATH</envar> "
"for some reason, modify the <envar>PATH</envar> in <filename>.bashrc</"
"filename> after LFS has been built."
msgstr ""
"Se você deseja incluir <filename class=\"directory\">/bin</filename> e (ou) "
"<filename class=\"directory\">/sbin</filename> no <envar>PATH</envar> por "
"alguma razão, [então] modifique a <envar>PATH</envar> em <filename>.bashrc</"
"filename> depois que o LFS tenha sido construído."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:83
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -e 's:#ENCRYPT_METHOD DES:ENCRYPT_METHOD YESCRYPT:' \\\n"
"    -e 's:/var/spool/mail:/var/mail:'                   \\\n"
"    -e '/PATH=/{s@/sbin:@@;s@/bin:@@}'                  \\\n"
"    -i etc/login.defs</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"pre\">sed -e 's:#ENCRYPT_METHOD DES:ENCRYPT_METHOD "
"YESCRYPT:' \\\n"
"    -e 's:/var/spool/mail:/var/mail:'                  \\\n"
"    -e '/PATH=/{s@/sbin:@@;s@/bin:@@}'                  \\\n"
"    -i etc/login.defs</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:89
msgid "If you chose to build Shadow with Cracklib support, issue this command:"
msgstr ""
"Se você escolher construir o Shadow com suporte a CrackLib, [então] emita "
"este comando:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><note><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:91
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>sed -i 's:DICTPATH.*:DICTPATH\\t/lib/cracklib/pw_dict:' etc/login.defs</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>sed -i 's:DICTPATH.*:DICTPATH\\t/lib/cracklib/pw_dict:' etc/login.defs</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:104
msgid "Prepare Shadow for compilation:"
msgstr "Prepare Shadow para compilação:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:106
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">touch /usr/bin/passwd\n"
"./configure --sysconfdir=/etc   \\\n"
"            --disable-static    \\\n"
"            --with-{b,yes}crypt \\\n"
"            --with-group-name-max-length=32</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput remap=\"configure\">touch /usr/bin/passwd\n"
"./configure --sysconfdir=/etc  \\\n"
"            --disable-static    \\\n"
"            --with-{b,yes}crypt \\\n"
"            --with-group-name-max-length=32</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><title>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:113
msgid "The meaning of the new configuration options:"
msgstr "O significado das novas opções de configuração:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:116
msgid "<command>touch /usr/bin/passwd</command>"
msgstr "<command>touch /usr/bin/passwd</command>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:118
msgid ""
"The file <filename>/usr/bin/passwd</filename> needs to exist because its "
"location is hardcoded in some programs; if it does not already exist, the "
"installation script will create it in the wrong place."
msgstr ""
"O arquivo <filename>/usr/bin/passwd</filename> precisa existir, pois o local "
"dele é codificado rigidamente em alguns aplicativos; se ele já não existir, "
"[então] o script de instalação o criará no lugar errado."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:126
msgid "<parameter>--with-{b,yes}crypt</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>--with-{b,yes}crypt</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:128
msgid ""
"The shell expands this to two switches, <parameter>--with-bcrypt</parameter> "
"and <parameter>--with-yescrypt</parameter>.  They allow shadow to use the "
"Bcrypt and Yescrypt algorithms implemented by <application>Libxcrypt</"
"application> for hashing passwords.  These algorithms are more secure (in "
"particular, much more resistant to GPU-based attacks) than the traditional "
"SHA algorithms."
msgstr ""
"O shell expande isso para duas chaves, <parameter>--with-bcrypt</parameter> "
"e <parameter>--with-yescrypt</parameter>. Elas permitem que o shadow use os "
"algoritmos Bcrypt e Yescrypt implementados pelo <application>Libxcrypt</"
"application> para resumir senhas. Esses algoritmos são mais seguros (em "
"particular, muito mais resistentes a ataques baseados em GPU) que os "
"algoritmos SHA tradicionais."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><term>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:140
msgid "<parameter>--with-group-name-max-length=32</parameter>"
msgstr "<parameter>--with-group-name-max-length=32</parameter>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><sect2><variablelist><varlistentry><listitem><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter08/shadow.xml:142
msgid ""
"The longest permissible user name is 32 characters.  Make the maximum length "
"of a group name the same."
msgstr ""
"O nome de usuária(o) mais longo permissível é o de trinta e dois (32) "
"caracteres. Torne o comprimento máximo de um nome de grupo o mesmo."

